Class KeyValueStoreData

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Future<KeyValueStoreQuery>, Associator, Eligible

    public class KeyValueStoreData
extends CompletionEvent<KeyValueStoreQuery>

    Defines an optional completion event for a KeyValueStoreQuery.

    Because KeyValueStoreQuery events have a result, this event is not automatically generated for every KeyValueStoreQuery. Rather, it must be created explicitly.
